title: Lewica Advisors

@leszek_miller
title: Leszek Miller
new-page: true
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/placeholder.jpg
tags: lewica_advisor
view-if: miller_advisor = 1

= Leszek Miller

Former prime minister, SLD chair, and the dominant figure of the 2014 party center. Miller is useful when the party needs discipline, parliamentary seriousness, or money, but his methods harden the younger and liberal-left wings.

- @miller_apparatus_discipline: Enforce apparatus discipline.
- @miller_emergency_fundraising: Emergency fundraising.
- @miller_coalition_respectability: Present SLD as the responsible governing left.
- @root: Return to main.

@miller_apparatus_discipline
title: Enforce Apparatus Discipline
subtitle: Reduce apparatus tension; raises modernizer and TR tension.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: {!
Q.advisor_action_timer = 6;
Q.advisor_last_action = "Miller: apparatus discipline";
Q.month_actions += 1;
Q.sld_apparatus_tension = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_tension - 18);
Q.sld_apparatus_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_strength + 0.4);
Q.sld_modernizers_tension = Math.min(150, Q.sld_modernizers_tension + 8);
Q.gawkowski_network_tension = Math.min(150, Q.gawkowski_network_tension + 6);
Q.tr_residue_tension = Math.min(150, Q.tr_residue_tension + 6);
!}

Miller leans on the regional chairs and the Sejm club. The apparatus quiets down, but reformers read it as another month of central-office rule.

- @post_event: Continue.

@miller_emergency_fundraising
title: Emergency Fundraising
subtitle: +2 resources; repeated use strains the party.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: {!
Q.advisor_action_timer = 6;
Q.advisor_last_action = "Miller: emergency fundraising";
Q.month_actions += 1;
Q.emergency_fundraising_used += 1;
Q.resources = Math.min(10, Q.resources + 2);
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
if (Q.emergency_fundraising_used > 1) {
    Q.sld_apparatus_tension = Math.min(150, Q.sld_apparatus_tension + 6);
    Q.sld_modernizers_tension = Math.min(150, Q.sld_modernizers_tension + 8);
    Q.tr_residue_tension = Math.min(150, Q.tr_residue_tension + 8);
    Q.pps_up_tension = Math.min(150, Q.pps_up_tension + 6);
    Q.urban_working_class_left = Math.max(0, Q.urban_working_class_left - 0.5);
    Q.under_30_left = Math.max(0, Q.under_30_left - 0.5);
}
!}

The old donor and local-government network can still produce cash. If used too often, members start to feel that survival is replacing politics.

- @post_event: Continue.

@miller_coalition_respectability
title: Responsible Governing Left
subtitle: Improve PO and PSL channels.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: {!
Q.advisor_action_timer = 6;
Q.advisor_last_action = "Miller: coalition respectability";
Q.month_actions += 1;
Q.ko_relation += 4;
Q.psl_relation += 2;
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.8 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.age_65_plus_left += 0.6 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.sld_apparatus_tension = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_tension - 8);
Q.tr_residue_tension = Math.min(150, Q.tr_residue_tension + 5);
Q.pps_up_tension = Math.min(150, Q.pps_up_tension + 4);
!}

The message is that SLD knows how to govern and will not burn down institutions for attention. It comforts older voters and coalition insiders.

- @post_event: Continue.

