= Krzysztof Gawkowski

Secretary-general, organizer, and a younger technocratic face of the SLD machine. Gawkowski works best where structure and modernization need to be reconciled.

- @gawkowski_secretary_map: Secretary's map.
- @gawkowski_modernization: Procedural modernization.
- @gawkowski_unity_calendar: Draft a unity calendar.
- @root: Return to main.

@gawkowski_secretary_map
title: Secretary's Map
subtitle: Regional rebuild and lower apparatus tension.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: {!
Q.advisor_action_timer = 6;
Q.advisor_last_action = "Gawkowski: secretary map";
Q.month_actions += 1;
Q.left_regional_rebuild += 1;
Q.sld_apparatus_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_strength + 0.3);
Q.sld_modernizers_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_strength + 0.2);
Q.gawkowski_network_strength = Math.min(10, Q.gawkowski_network_strength + 0.4);
