= Wanda Nowicka

Former deputy speaker and feminist organizer from the Palikot-era liberal-left orbit. Nowicka gives the SLD access to women's-rights and parliamentary-bridge credibility.

- @nowicka_feminist_bridge: Feminist parliamentary bridge.
- @nowicka_reproductive_frame: Reproductive rights frame.
- @nowicka_liberal_left_channel: Liberal-left channel.
- @root: Return to main.

@nowicka_feminist_bridge
title: Feminist Parliamentary Bridge
subtitle: Women under 50 and civil society.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: {!
Q.advisor_action_timer = 6;
Q.advisor_last_action = "Nowicka: feminist bridge";
Q.month_actions += 1;
Q.women_under_50_left += 1.4 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.civil_society_capital = Math.min(10, Q.civil_society_capital + 0.5);
Q.tr_residue_tension = Math.max(0, Q.tr_residue_tension - 7);
Q.sld_apparatus_tension = Math.min(150, Q.sld_apparatus_tension + 4);
!}

The party reconnects with activists who do not trust SLD automatically but need parliamentary allies.

- @post_event: Continue.

