title: United Left Public Face
subtitle: Brand boost and partner cohesion; apparatus tension rises.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0 and year >= 2015
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?][? if year < 2015 : This action belongs to the 2015 unity campaign. ?]
